WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.040 --> 00:00:11.000
Now what do we mean by home automation?
Could it be this?

00:00:11.720 --> 00:00:15.600
[SYNTH VOICE] Are you eating again? 
No wonder you're getting fat.

00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:18.320
[SYNTH VOICE] Your toast is ready.

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:22.460
[SYNTH VOICE] The kettle has boiled. 
That is enough for two cups.

00:00:22.920 --> 00:00:26.680
[SYNTH VOICES OVERLAP] The kettle has boiled. 
The egg whites are stiffly beaten.

00:00:26.680 --> 00:00:38.540
[MULTIPLE SYNTH VOICES OVERLAP 
AND SOUND IS DISTORTED]

00:00:38.540 --> 00:00:42.700
[SYNTH VOICE] Remember to lock the door.

00:00:42.700 --> 00:00:44.580
[SYNTH VOICE] You have left the light on.

00:00:44.780 --> 00:00:45.860
[SYNTH VOICE] Thank you.

00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:52.640
Isn't that horrible? I can assure you that home automation does not mean what that film clip showed.

